%20final%20against%20England%20on%20Sunday%2C%20was%20informed%20about%20her%20father's%20death%20just%20after%20the%20match%20ended%2C%20the%20Spanish%20FA%20said%20on%20social%20media.%20According%20to%20the%20media%20release%20by%20the%20Spanish%20FA%2C%20Carmona's%20father%20was%20struggling%20with%20illness%20for%20some%20time%20and%20although%20he%20died%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20not%20inform%20her%20of%20the%20incident%20before%20the%20World%20Cup%20final.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20you%20have%20given%20me%20the%20strength%20to%20achieve%20something%20unique%2C%26quot%3B%20Carmona%20wrote%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20you%20have%20been%20watching%20me%20tonight%20and%20that%20you%20are%20proud%20of%20me.%20Rest%20in%20peace%2C%20dad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%3EY%20sin%20saberlo%20ten%C3%ADa%20mi%20Estrella%20antes%20de%20que%20empezase%20el%20partido.%20S%C3%A9%20que%20me%20has%20dado%20la%20fuerza%20para%20conseguir%20algo%20%C3%BAnico.%20S%C3%A9%20que%20me%20has%20estado%20viendo%20esta%20noche%20y%20que%20est%C3%A1s%20orgulloso%20de%20m%C3%AD.%20Descansa%20en%20paz%2C%20pap%C3%A1%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUby0mteZQ3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FUby0mteZQ3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Olga%20Carmona%20(%407olgacarmona)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F7olgacarmona%2Fstatus%2F1693396084201337008%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain%C2%A0won%20the%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20their%20history%20with%20skipper%20Olga%20Carmona%20striking%20in%20the%20first%20half%20for%20a%20deserved%201-0%20victory%20over%20England%20in%20Sunday's%20final.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gripping%20encounter%20was%20a%20fitting%20conclusion%20to%20a%20tournament%20in%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20which%20has%20broken%20records%20and%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20how%20the%20supposed%20minnows%20closed%20the%20gap%20on%20the%20sides%20at%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20front%20of%20a%20packed%20crowd%20of%20nearly%2076%2C000%20at%20Stadium%20Australia%20in%20Sydney%2C%C2%A0Spain%C2%A0were%20the%20more%20accomplished%20side%C2%A0and%20had%20more%20chances%2C%20including%20missing%20a%20second-half%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain's%20triumph%20was%20vindication%20for%20Jorge%20Vilda%20and%20the%20Spanish%20football%20federation%2C%20who%20stuck%20with%20the%20coach%20even%20after%2015%20players%20last%20year%20said%20they%20no%20longer%20wanted%20to%20represent%20their%20country%20under%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefender%20Carmona%20scored%20what%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20winner%2C%20rampaging%20from%20left-back%20to%20thrash%20the%20ball%20in%20low%20and%20hard%20on%2029%20minutes%20past%20England%20goalkeeper%20Mary%20Earps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20describe%2C%20immense%20joy%2C%20I'm%20so%20proud%20of%20this%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2042-year-old%20Vilda%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20being%20too%20strict%2C%20among%20a%20litany%20of%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20smattering%20of%20boos%20when%20his%20image%20was%20put%20up%20at%20Stadium%20Australia%20during%20the%20game%20and%20again%20when%20he%20strode%20up%20to%20the%20podium%20before%C2%A0Spain%C2%A0lifted%20the%20trophy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20happy%20for%20everyone%20watching%20us%20right%20now%2C%20we've%20made%20them%20happy%20too.%20We're%20champions%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Vilda%2C%20who%20recalled%20three%20of%20the%2015%20mutineers%20for%20the%20tournament%20but%20left%20several%20top%20players%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20coach%20Sarina%20Wiegman%20has%20now%20suffered%20back-to-back%20defeats%20in%20the%20final%2C%20and%20her%20European%20champions%20can%20have%20few%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20front%20of%20the%20watching%20Queen%20Letizia%2C%C2%A0Spain%C2%A0won%20a%20penalty%2020%20minutes%20from%20the%20end%20when%20Keira%20Walsh%20was%20ruled%20to%20have%20handled%20in%20the%20box%20after%20a%20long%20VAR%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Jennifer%20Hermoso's%20weak%20penalty%20was%20easily%20saved%20by%20Earps%20to%20give%20England%20a%20lifeline%20and%20keep%20alive%20their%20dreams%20of%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20anything%2C%C2%A0Spain%C2%A0looked%20the%20more%20likely%20to%20score%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain's%20players%20raced%20off%20the%20bench%20at%20the%20final%20whistle%2C%20while%20England's%20players%20were%20left%20distraught%2C%20some%20with%20their%20heads%20in%20their%20hands%20and%20others%20in%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain%C2%A0are%20the%20fifth%20team%20to%20lift%20the%20World%20Cup%20since%20the%20tournament%20began%20in%201991%2C%20joining%20outgoing%20champions%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Germany%2C%20Norway%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20AFP%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692592920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Flalmetug_da_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffifa-women-s-world-cup-2023%2Fspains-goal-scorer-olga-carmona-told-about-fathers-death-just-after-womens-world-cup-final-4314738%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Spain%20won%20the%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20their%20history%20with%20skipper%20Olga%20Carmona%20striking%20in%20the%20first%20half.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffifa-women-s-world-cup-2023%2Fspains-goal-scorer-olga-carmona-told-about-fathers-death-just-after-womens-world-cup-final-4314738%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2