Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somashekar%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Yashwanthpur%20constituency%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20his%20meeting%20with%20Siddaramaiah%20at%20his%20residence%20was%20over%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bdevelopment%20of%20his%20constituency%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20said%20the%20meeting%20was%20regarding%20the%20need%20for%20a%20maternity%20hospital%20at%20Sir%20M%20Visvesvaraya%20Layout%20on%20a%20civic%20amenity%20plot%20and%20a%20flyover%20for%20Kengeri%20Satellite%20Town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somashekar%20has%20been%20meeting%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20recent%20days%20and%20had%20even%20praised%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20as%20his%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20guru%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20another%20development%2C%20JD(S)%20leader%20Ayanur%20Manjunath%20called%20on%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20state%20chief%20DK%20Shivakumar%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20meeting%20with%20Manjunath%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20said%20many%20people%20meet%20him%20and%20that%20he%20cannot%20explain%20the%20reason%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20'Operation%20Hasta'%2C%20referring%20to%20Congress's%20hand%20symbol%2C%20has%20gained%20significance%20as%20it%20is%20said%20to%20be%20a%20drive%20to%20bring%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20legislators%20to%20the%20Congress%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Operation%20Hasta'%20is%20said%20to%20be%20in%20retaliation%20to%20the%20BJP's%20'Operation%20Lotus'%20in%202019%20when%2017%20Congress%20and%20JD(S)%20legislators%20jumped%20ship%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%20'Op%20Lotus'%20had%20resulted%20in%20the%20toppling%20of%20the%20short-lived%20coalition%20government%20of%20Congress%20and%20the%20JD(S).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20rumours%20doing%20rounds%20that%20many%20BJP%20legislators%20and%20leaders%20are%20said%20to%20be%20in%20touch%20with%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20started%20an%20exercise%20to%20keep%20its%20flock%20together%20and%20are%20trying%20to%20persuade%20its%20disgruntled%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20ago%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20and%20former%20ministers%20Shivaram%20Hebbar%20and%20Munirathna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20to%20them%20and%20they%20clearly%20said%20they%20are%20not%20going%20to%20quit%20the%20party.%20We%20have%20brought%20the%20local%20problems%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20our%20party%20president.%20That%20will%20be%20solved.%20We%20will%20remain%20united%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bommai%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20angry%20rebuttal%20to%20'Operation%20Hasta'%20came%20from%20former%20minister%20and%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20CT%20Ravi%20who%20said%20he%20knew%20how%20to%20%26quot%3Boperate%20the%20palm%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shivakumar%20responded%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BCT%20Ravi%20is%20giving%20us%20a%20threat%20that%20he%20will%20chop%20off%20the%20palm.%20What%20happened%20when%20you%20(BJP)%20took%20away%20Congress%20and%20JD(S)%20MLAs%3F%20When%20you%20can%20threaten%20others%2C%20others%20also%20know%20how%20to%20threaten%20you.%20You%20brought%20down%20the%20coalition%20government%20to%20form%20yours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clarified%20that%20he%20is%20not%20calling%20anyone%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20now%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692591180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fp569d6tg_siddaramaiah-budget_625x300_07_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fbjp-ex-minister-s-t-somashekar-meets-siddaramaiah-amid-buzz-over-defected-leaders-return-4314224%22%2C%22summary%22%3