two%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20say%20it%20would%20be%20changed%20for%20sure%20but%20back%20to%20back%20games%20are%20not%20ideal.%20I%20mean%20if%20they%20(BCCI)%20are%20reconsidering%20that%20will%20be%20well%20and%20good.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20work%20with%20security%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20would%20want%20a%20day%20in%20between%20two%20World%20Cup%20games.%20We%20are%20still%20engaging%20with%20security%20agencies%20to%20see%20if%20it%20is%20possible%20or%20not.%20At%20the%20same%20time%20we%20are%20also%20keeping%20BCCI%20in%20the%20loop.%20The%20BCCI%20is%20completely%20aware%20of%20what%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20HCA%20official%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Shukla%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement%20that%20no%20further%20changes%20are%20likely%20as%20it%20requires%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20in%20charge%20of%20Hyderabad%20venue%20for%20WC.%20If%20there%20will%20be%20any%20issue%20or%20anything%2C%20will%20try%20to%20get%20it%20resolved.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20change%20the%20World%20Cup%20schedule%20and%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20happen.%20Only%20BCCI%20can't%20change%20schedule%2C%20teams%2C%20ICC%2C%20all%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shukla%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%20For%20an%20international%20game%2C%20the%20Hyderabad%20Police%20deploys%20between%202000-2500%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeployment%20also%20depends%20on%20nature%20of%20the%20game%20and%20how%20many%20people%20turn%20up.%20Police%20makes%20those%20assessments%20and%20deploys%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HCA%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20Pakistan's%20involvement%20in%20one%20of%20those%20games%2C%20the%20security%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20heightened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%2C%20who%20will%20play%20in%20India%20for%20the