C%20if%20India%20charges%20us%20--%20India%20is%20very%20big%20with%20tariffs.%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20saw%20it%20with%20Harley-Davidson.%20I%20was%20saying%2C%20how%20do%20you%20do%20in%20a%20place%20like%20India%3F%20Oh%2C%20no%20good%20sir.%20Why%3F%20They%20have%20100%20per%20cent%20and%20150%20per%20cent%20and%20200%20per%20cent%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20said%2C%20so%20they%20can%20sell%20their%20Indian%20motorbike.%20They%20actually%20make%20a%20bike%2C%20an%20Indian%20motorbike.%20They%20can%20sell%20that%20into%20our%20country%20with%20no%20tax%2C%20no%20tariff%2C%20but%20when%20you%20make%20a%20Harley%2C%20when%20you%20send%20it%20over%20there%20--%20because%20they%20were%20doing%20no%20business.%20I%20said%2C%20how%20come%20you%20don't%20do%20business%20with%20India%3F%20The%20tariff%20is%20so%20high%20that%20nobody%20wants%20it.%20But%20what%20they%20want%20us%20to%20do%20is%2C%20they%20want%20us%20to%20go%20over%20and%20build%20a%20plant%2C%20and%20then%20you%20have%20no%20tariff%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%2C%20well%2C%20that's%20not%20good.%20That's%20not%20our%20deal%2C%20OK%3F%20That's%20not%20our%20deal.%20And%20I%20came%20down%20very%20hard%20on%20them.%20But%20India%20is%20very%20big.%20Brazil%20is%20very%20big%20on%20tariffs%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20very%2C%20very%20big.%20We%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20people%2C%20like%20the%20senator%20from%20a%20place%20called%20Pennsylvania%20that%20I%20love.%20But%20this%20guy%20was%20just%20horrendous.%20I%20said%2C%20let%20me%20ask%20you%20a%20question.%20If%20India%20is%20charging%20us%20200%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20we're%20charging%20them%20nothing%20for%20products%2C%20can%20we%20charge%20them%20100%20per%20cent%3F%20No%2C%20sir%2C%20that's%20not%20free%20trade.%20Can%20we%20charge%20them%2050%20per%20cent%3F%20No%2C%20sir.%20Twenty-five%2C%2010%2C%20anything%3F%20No.%20I%20said%2C%20what%20the%20hell%20is%20wrong%3F%20There's%20something%20wrong.%20You%20know%20what%20I'm%20talking%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20India%20is%20charging%20us%20too%2C%20so%20what%20I%20want%20to%20have%20is%20a%20--%20call%20it%20retribution.%20You%20could%20call%20it%20whatever%20you%20want.%20If%20they%20are%20charging%20us%2C%20we%20charge%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%2C%20who%20is%20facing%20a%20series%20of%20court%20cases%20and%20indictments%2C%20is%20leading%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20primaries%2C%20and%20accounts%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20GOP%20votes%20according%20to%20major%20national%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692587460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F7m0a05lg_donald-trump-afp_625x300_14_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdonald-trump-reiterates-reciprocal-tax-on-india-if-he-returns-as-us-president-4314576%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20seeking%20his%20term%2C%20has%20once%20again%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20high%20tax%20by%20India%20on%20certain%20American%20products%20and%20has%20said%20he'd%20slap%20reciprocal%20tax%20if%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdonald-trump-reiterates-reciprocal-tax-on-india-if-he-returns-as-us-president-4314576%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdonald-trump-reiterates-reciprocal-tax-on-india-if-he-returns-as-us-president-4314576%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampU