t%20he%20made%20several%20achievements%20in%20the%20short%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20the%20service%20of%20the%20country%2C%20including%20towards%20women%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajiv%20Gandhi's%20political%20career%20was%20finished%20in%20a%20brutal%20manner%20but%20he%20achieved%20many%20milestones%20in%20that%20short%20time.%20He%20was%20very%20sensitive%20towards%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20country.%20Whatever%20time%20he%20got%20to%20serve%20the%20nation%2C%20he%20accomplished%20uncountable%20achievements.%20He%20was%20dedicated%20towards%20women's%20empowerment.%20He%20struggled%20for%20the%201%2F3%20reservation%20of%20women%20in%20Panchayat%20and%20Municipals.%20If%20today%2C%20over%2015%20lakh%20elected%20women%20representatives%20are%20there%20in%20rural%20and%20urban%20bodies%2C%20it%20is%20only%20because%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20hard%20work%20and%20far-sightedness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sonia%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20government%20also%20lowered%20the%20age%20of%20voting%20to%2018%20years%20from%2021%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Gandhi%20took%20over%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%201984%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20his%20mother%20and%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20India's%20youngest%20Prime%20Minister%20at%20the%20age%20of%2040%20when%20he%20assumed%20office%20in%20October%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20served%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20till%20December%202%2C%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20on%20August%2020%20in%201944%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20assassinated%20by%20a%20Liberation%20Tigers%20of%20Tamil%20Eelam%20(LTTE)%20suicide%20bomber%20during%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Sriperumbudur%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20on%20May%2021%2C%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20vice%20president%20M%20Hamid%20Ansari%20on%20Sunday%20conferred%20the%2025th%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20National%20Sadbhavana%20Award%20for%202020-21%20on%20Banasthali%20Vidyapith%2C%20a%20residential%20institution%20for%20women%20in%20Rajasthan.%20The%20award%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20Siddhartha%20Shastri%20of%20the%20institution%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Congress%20Parliamentary%20Party%20chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20further%20said%20that%20the%20ideals%20of%20communal%20harmony%2C%20peace%20and%20national%20unity%20have%20become%20more%20significant%20in%20these%20present%20times%20when%20the%20forces%20giving%20rise%20to%20hatred%2C%20division%20in%20society%2C%20bigotry%20and%20politics%20of%20bias%20are%20getting%20more%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20also%20getting%20the%20support%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20other%20party%20leaders%20on%20Sunday%20attended%20the%2025th%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20National%20Sadbhavana%20Award%20event%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20held%20at%20Jawahar%20Bhawan%20in%20Delhi%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20former%20PM's%2079th%20birth%20anniversary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20further%20said%20that%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%C2%A0was%20a%20supporter%20of%20the%20protection%20and%20conservation%20of%20polymorphism%20present%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20very%20sensitive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20unity%20of%20India%20can%20be%20strengthened%20only%20by%20celebrating%20religious%2C%20ethnic%2C%20languages%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8Band%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20paid%20floral%20tribute%20to%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20his%2079th%20birth%20anniversary%20at%20'Veer%20Bhumi'%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20General%20Secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Robert%20Vadra%20and%20Congress%20National%20President%20Mallikarju