ilies%20did%20not%20receive%20the%20verdicts%20they%20had%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20babies%20Letby%20was%20accused%20of%20attacking%20were%20twins.%20A%20baby%20boy%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20child%20A%2C%20was%20just%20a%20day%20old%20when%20he%20died%20in%20early%20June%202015%2C%20while%20his%20elder%20sister%20survived%20a%20murder%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20two%20triplet%20brothers%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20each%20other%20in%20June%202016%2C%20Letby%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20neonatal%20unit%20and%20placed%20on%20clerical%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20in%20July%202018%2C%20she%20was%20arrested%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20On%20her%20third%20arrest%20in%20November%202020%2C%20Letby%20was%20formally%20charged%20and%20placed%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby's%20motives%20remain%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20the%20prosecution%20described%20Letby%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcalculating%26quot%3B%20woman%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bgaslighted%26quot%3B%20her%20colleagues%20into%20believing%20the%20rise%20in%20baby%20deaths%20was%20%26quot%3Bjust%20a%20run%20of%20bad%20luck%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20was%20told%20that%20Letby%20was%20on%20shift%20when%20each%20of%20the%20babies%20collapsed.%20Some%20of%20the%20newborns%20were%20attacked%20just%20as%20their%20parents%20left%20their%20cots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20that%20Letby%20took%20an%20unusual%20interest%20in%20the%20families%20of%20her%20victims%2C%20making%20searches%20for%20them%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20sent%20a%20sympathy%20card%20to%20the%20grieving%20parents%20of%20a%20child%20she%20was%20later%20found%20guilty%20of%20murdering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHandwritten%20notes%20found%20during%20police%20searches%20at%20Letby's%20home%20were%20among%20the%20evidence%20seen%20by%20the%20court%2C%20one%20of%20which%20had%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20evil%20I%20did%20this%26quot%3B%20written%20in%20capital%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetby%20denied%20harming%20the%20babies%20and%20claimed%20a%20group%20of%20four%20senior%20doctors%20tried%20to%20pin%20blame%20on%20her%20to%20cover%20for%20the%20hospital's%20shortcomings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20government%20has%20announced%20an%20independent%20enquiry%20into%20the%20case%20and%20will%20look%20at%20how%20the%20concerns%20of%20clinicians%20were%20dealt%20with%20by%20hospital%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692582600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbr77oh3s_lucy-letby-afp_625x300_19_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-killer-nurse-faces-life-sentence-for-murdering-7-babies-4314555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20British%20nurse%20will%20be%20sentenced%20on%20Monday%20for%20murdering%20seven%20newborn%20babies%20and%20attempting%20to%20kill%20six%20others%20while%20they%20were%20in%20her%20care.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-killer-nurse-faces-life-sentence-for-murdering-7-babies-4314555%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-killer-nurse-faces-life-sentence-for-murdering-7-babies-4314555%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-killer-nurse-faces-life-sentence-for-murdering-7-babies-4314555%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRSS%20Ravi%26quot%3B%3A%20MK%20Stalin's%20Son%20Slams%20Governor%20Over%20Bill%20To%20Abolish%20NEET%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDMK%20youth%20wing%20state%20secretary%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20on%20Sunday%20hit%20out%20a