20burial%20plots%20scarce%2C%20and%20pricey.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETo%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%20Beijing%20has%20started%20encouraging%20people%20to%20grieve%20their%20loved%20ones%20in%20digital%20funeral%20spaces%20instead%20of%20traditional%20burial%20sites%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2023-08-15%2Fchina-pilots-digital-burials-and-funeral-services-as-population-ages%3Fsrnd%3Dbusinessweek-v2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20recent%20report%20from%20Bloomberg.%20The%20State%20Council%20said%20that%20by%202035%2C%20Beijing%20will%20try%20to%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20land%20public%20cemeteries%20occupy%20by%2070%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20a%20digital%20burial%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Beijing's%20Taiziyu%20Cemetery%20there%20are%20compartments%20for%20storing%20ashes%20that%20also%20display%20digital%20pictures%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20dead%20on%20their%20doors%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%20Since%20the%20start%20of%202023%2C%20more%20than%20500%20digital%20plots%20like%20these%20have%20been%20sold%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%2C%20citing%20Beijing%20Jiuli%20Digital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20also%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20burial%26quot%3B%20program%20where%20ashes%20of%20the%20deceased%20can%20be%20buried%20without%20a%20gravestone%20or%20mausoleum%20for%20free%2C%20and%20relatives%20will%20receive%20a%20commemorative%20plaque%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20they%20can%20scan%20to%20access%20the%20information%20of%20the%20deceased%20at%20any%20time%2C%20CGTN%2C%20a%20local%20state-run%20news%20channel%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cgtn.com%2Fnews%2F3d677a4d78497a4d%2Fshare_p.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(The%20government%20has%20also%20sponsored%20initiatives%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-pushes-burial-at-sea-2013-4%5C%22%3Eencourage%20families%20to%20scatter%20ashes%20at%20sea%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20is%20not%20the%20only%20city%20where%20digital%20burials%20are%20gaining%20traction.%20In%20Shanghai%2C%20an%20online%20mausoleum%20called%20Fu%20Shou%20Yuan%20that%20recently%20opened%20allows%20people%20to%20conduct%20virtual%20burials%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%20Fu%20Shou%20Yuan's%20%26quot%3BHeaven%20on%20the%20Cloud%26quot%3B%20project%20lets%20people%20create%20%26quot%3Bvirtual%20islands%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20loved%20ones'%20pictures%2C%20digital%20assets%2C%20and%20sound%20files%2C%20Bloomberg%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDigital%20funerals%20save%20money%20and%20space%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sunlife.co.uk%2Fover-50-life-insurance%2Ffuneral-costs%2Finternational-cost-of-dying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20SunLife%2C%20a%20UK-based%20life%20insurance%20company%2C%20the%20average%20funeral%20in%20China%20costs%20about%20%245%2C400%2C%20and%20people%20spend%20more%20than%2045%25%20of%20their%20average%20annual%20salary%20on%20them.%20(For%20context%3A%20Those%20in%20the%20United%20States%20spend%20a%20little%20more%20than%2012%25%20of%20their%20salary%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuneral-industry-costs-rising-cremation-services-2023-7%5C%22%3Efunerals%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20the%20global%20rate%20is%2010%25%2C%20according%20to%20SunLife's%20report).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20burial%20rates%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeijing-new-york-city-billionaires-comparison-2021-4%5C%22%3Ecountry's%20capital%20of%20Beijing%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20go%20far%20beyond%20that.%20A%20digital%20burial%20at%20Beijing's%20Taiziyu%20Cemetery%20costs%20more%20than%20%247%2C700%2C%20which%20is%20a%20third%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20an%20outdoor%20burial%20plot%20in%20the%20same%20area%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20burials%20save%20space%2C%20too.%20A%20digital%20cemetery%20that's%20about%20215%20square%20feet%20can%20house%20more%20than%20150%20plots%2C%20while%20a%20site%20that%20size%20might%20only%20house%20six%20traditional%20gravesites%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeijing-is-encouraging-digital-funerals-over-traditional-burials-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692558224000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e25783bd98a600197a5831%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeijing-is-encouraging-digital-funerals-over-traditional-burials-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Beijing%20is%20encouraging%20digital%20burials%20in%20favor%20of%20traditional%20ones%20as%20urban%20land%20becomes%20increasingly%20scarce%20and%20expensive%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeijing-is-encouraging-digital-funerals-over-traditional-burials-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttarakhand%20sacks%206%20govt%20lawyers%20for%20'vacillating%20attitude%20in%20HC'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692557895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102881160%2Cimgsize-34590.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Futtarakhand-sacks-6-govt-lawyers-for-vacillating-attitude-in-hc%2Farticleshow%2F102881146.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20order%20was%20issued%20by%20additional%20secretary%20Sudhir%20Kumar%20Singh.%20It%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BAppointment