20room%20during%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Civita%20Giuliana%20Roman%20villa%2C%20located%20around%20600%20meters%20outside%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20famous%20city%20that%20was%20destroyed%20when%20Mount%20Vesuvius%20erupted%20in%2079%20AD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20contained%20two%20beds%20%E2%80%94%20only%20one%20of%20which%20had%20a%20mattress%20%E2%80%94%20basic%20cabinets%2C%20and%20containers%20that%20had%20the%20remains%20of%20rats%20and%20mice%20inside%2C%20the%20Italian%20culture%20ministry%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bdetails%20that%20underscore%20the%20precarious%20and%20unhygienic%20conditions%20in%20which%20the%20lower%20echelons%20of%20society%20lived.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20find%20also%20offered%20an%20insight%20into%20the%20social%20hierarchy%20in%20ancient%20Rome%2C%20as%20the%20culture%20ministry%20noted%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20of%20locks%20or%20shackles%20discovered%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20that%20control%20was%20established%20mainly%20through%20the%20internal%20organization%20of%20servitude%2C%20and%20not%20through%20barriers%20and%20physical%20constraints%2C%26quot%3B%20Gabriel%20Zuchtriegel%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Pompeii%20archaeological%20park%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20bedroom%2C%20that%20was%20almost%20certainly%20used%20by%20slaves%2C%20is%20pictured%20after%20it%20was%20discovered%20by%20archaeologists%20in%20a%20Roman%20villa%20near%20Pompeii%2C%20in%20this%20undated%20picture%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e24ae1bd98a600197a5659%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20small%20bedroom%2C%20used%20by%20slaves%2C%20is%20pictured%20after%20it%20was%20discovered%20by%20archaeologists%20in%20a%20Roman%20villa%20near%20Pompeii%2C%20Italy.%3Cp%3EUfficio%20Stampa%20e%20Comunicazione%20MiC%2FHandout%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcap