ering%20unsung%20heroes%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20guest%20at%20the%20show%20was%20Hindi%20writer%20Rajendra%20Rajan%2C%20who%20penned%20a%20book%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flipkart.com%2Funsung-composer-ina-captain-ram-singh-thakur-jang-gan-man-ke-janak%2Fp%2Fitm0707027bbb0a8%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Unsung%20Composer%20of%20INA%3A%20Captain%20Ram%20Singh%20Thakur%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Father%20Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%202021%2C%20it%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.punjabnewsexpress.com%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fcm-releases-book-of-rajendra-rajan-on-ina-soldier-captain-ram-singh-153490%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereleased%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20state%20Thakuri%20belonged%20to.%20While%20Rajan%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20%E2%80%98Thakur%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20book%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20show%2C%20Ram%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20surname%20was%20Thakuri%2C%20a%20surname%20common%20among%20the%20Gorkha%20community%20of%20India%20and%20Nepal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTextbooks%20in%20all%20schools%20across%20the%20country%20inform%20that%20Tagore%20composed%20the%20lyrics%20but%20none%20mentions%20who%20composed%20the%20music.%20This%20needs%20to%20come%20on%20record%20so%20that%20we%20do%20not%20forget%20Ram%20Singh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20such%20a%20claim%20has%20been%20made.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20described%20him%20in%20a%20social%20media%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMIB_India%2Fstatus%2F1647155311021821954%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epost%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20person%20who%20%E2%80%9Ccomposed%20the%20INA%20anthem%20%E2%80%98Qaumi%20Tarana%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%20Rajan%20himself%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df_PAAy1cOWM%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20featured%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20public%20service%20broadcaster%E2%80%99s%20DD%20Himachal%20channel%E2%80%99s%20Bhagdhara%20show%20last%20year%2C%20where%20they%20made%20the%20same%20claim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20Times%20Now%E2%80%99s%20TN%20Plus%2C%20in%20a%20video%20report%2C%20said%20Thakuri%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20forever%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20the%20man%20who%20composed%20the%20tune%20for%20the%20Indian%20national%20anthem%2C%20whose%20lyrics%20have%20been%20penned%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdainikchintak.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14-8-2023-1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esame%C2%A0%20claim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.divyahimachal.com%2F2023%2F08%2Fthe-forgotten-creator-of-the-tune-of-jana-gana-mana%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emade%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Hindi%20writer%20Dharampal%20Sahil%20and%20multiple%20Gorkha-centric%20websites%20as%20well.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Findependence-day-national-anthem-jana-gana-mana-subhash-chandra-bose-netaji%5C%22%3E%20How%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Why%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20Became%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20Anthem%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20DD%20Morning%20Show%2C%20Rajan%20said%20that%20Thakuri%20himself%20told%20him%20about%20the%20history%20of%20creating%20the%20%E2%80%98Qaumi%20Tarana%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20which%20Rajan%20equated%20with%20the%20national%20anthem.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose-led%20Indian%20National%20Army%20(INA)%E2%80%99s%20Lieutenant-Colonel%20Lakhsmi%20Sehgal%20had%20mentioned%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20when%20Netaji%20asked%20for%20an%20anthem%20but%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20song%20required%20to%20be%20simplified%20because%20it%20was%20highly%20Sanskritised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThereafter%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbid%20Ali%20Safrani%20and%20Mumtaz%20Hussain%2C%20scriptwriters%20associated%20with%20the%20INA%E2%80%99s%20Radio%20Singapore%2C%20created%20a%20simplified%20version%E2%80%9D%2C%20starting%20as%20%E2%80%98Subh%20Sukh%20Chain%20Ki%20Barkha%20Barshe%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Thakuri%20was%20asked%20to%20set%20it%20to%20tune%2C%20which%20he%20did%20in%20a%20week%2C%20Rajan%20said.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20it%20remained%20as%20the%20INA%20or%20Azad%20Hind%20Fauz%E2%80%99s%20national%20anthem%20for%20five-six%20months%2C%20as%20the%20organisation%2C%20on%20January%201%2C%201944%2C%20decided%20to%20revert%20to%20the%20lyrics%20of%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20national%20anthem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20presenters%20asked%20Rajan%20to%20describe%20how%20the%20original%20song%20was.%20Rajan%20did%20not%20say%20anything%20on%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99.%20The%20presenters%20then%20played%20an%20old%20video%20showing%20Thakuri%20playing%20the%20violin%20in%20a%20rendition%20of%20%E2%80%98Subh%20Sukh%20Chain%E2%80%99%20and%20informed%20the%20audience%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20original.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F14190413%2Fnetaji-jana-gana-mana.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F14190413%2Fnetaji-jana-gana-mana.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F14190413%2Fnetaji-jana-gana-mana-300x195.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-473193%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDelhi%2C%201945.%20Capt.%20Ram%20Singh%20Thakuri%20and%20other%20Azad%20Hind%20POWs%20sing%20the%20National%20Anthem%20during%20a%20visit%20by%20Gandhiji.%3Cbr%3ESource%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fthedarjeelingchronicle.com%2Fspecial-article-capt-ram-singh-thakuri%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20these%20claims%20are%20baseless.%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20anthem%20is%20no%20different%20than%20how%20Tagore%20had%20set%20it%20to%20tune.%20It%20was%20first%20performed%20in%20public%20in%20December%2C%201911%20at%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%2026th%20annual%20session%20in%20Kolkata.%20Multiple%20records%20of%20the%20songs%20had%20been%20released%20much%20before%20the%20INA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Qaumi%20Tarana%E2%80%99%20was%20composed%20in%20Singapore%20in%201943.%20The%20associated%20history%20is%20quite%20well-known%20in%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20earliest%20recording%20of%20the%20song%20was%20released%20in%201934%20when%20Hindusthan%20Records%20published%20(record%20number%20H%20191)%20two%20Tagore%20songs%20on%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20disc%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20on%20one%20and%20%E2%80%98Ekla%20Chalo%20Re%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20other.%20They%20were%20chorus%20renditions%20by%20Amala%20Dutta%2C%20Nandita%20Devi%2C%20Sudhin%20Dutta%2C%20and%20Santi%20Ghosh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20also%20famous%20as%20the%20first%20song%20ever%20recorded%20by%20the%20legendary%20Rabindra%20Sangeet%20exponent%20Santidev%20Ghosh.%20His%20original%20name%20was%20Santimoy%20but%20he%20used%20only%20Santi%20in%20those%20days%2C%20until%20Tagore%20gave%20him%20the%20name%20Santidev%20in%20the%20mid-1930s.%20Ghosh%20used%20Santidev%20till%20his%20death%20in%201999.%20Ghosh%20was%20a%20young%20music%20teacher%20at%20Visva%20Bharati%20when%20this%20was%20recorded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20others%2C%20Nandita%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Tagore%20family%20and%20Amala%20and%20Sudhin%20were%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20music%20students.%20Nandita%20was%20one%20of%20those%20who%20joined%20Sucheta%20Kripalani%20in%20singing%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20at%20midnight%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%E2%80%99s%20central%20hall%2C%20according%20to%20Chitra%20Deb%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThakur%20Barir%20Andarmahal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(Inside%20the%20Tagore%20residence).%20Thanks%20to%20digitisation%2C%20the%20recording%20has%20now%20become%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrUQQ9rc0874%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eavailable%20online%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20recording%20of%20the%20song%20was%20released%20in%20December%201937%2C%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Congress%20adopting%20a%20truncated%20version%20of%20Bankim%20Chandra%20Chattopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Bande%20Mataram%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20national%20anthem%20after%20intense%20nationwide%20debate%20over%20choosing%20between%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Bande%20Mataram%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20disc%2C%20also%20released%20by%20Hindusthan%20Records%2C%20had%20the%20two%20songs%20on%20two%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETagore%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20publicly%20perform%20%E2%80%98Bande%20Mataram%E2%80%99%20in%201896%20and%20trained%20the%20singers%20himself%20for%20this%20recording%2C%20the%20label%20on%20the%20record%20states.%20The%20literature%20published%20along%20with%20the%20record%20attributes%20%E2%80%98Bande%20Mataram%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20music%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress-e%20procholito%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bengali%20word%20%E2%80%98Procholito%E2%80%99%20can%20be%20translated%20as%20traditional%20or%20conventional.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20attribution%20means%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20sung%20in%20the%20tune%20that%20is%20traditional%20or%20conventional%20in%20the%20Congress%20culture.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20the%20identity%20of%20%E2%80%98Vande%20Mataram%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20music%20composer%20remains%20a%20topic%20of%20debate.%20However%2C%20for%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%2C%20both%20lyrics%20and%20music%20were%20attributed%20to%20Tagore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20songs%20were%20in%20chorus%20by%20Prova%20Ray%2C%20Jaya%20Das%2C%20Bejoya%20Devi%2C%20Dhiren%20Gupta%2C%20and%20Haripada%20Chatterjee.%20Of%20them%2C%20Ray%20is%20filmmaker%20Satyajit%20Ray%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20originally%20Suprabha%2C%20and%20Bejoya%20Devi%20is%20none%20other%20than%20Satyajit%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Bijoya%20Ray.%20Bijoya%20mentioned%20this%20recording%20in%20her%20memoir.%20The%20Ray%20family%20was%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20Tagore%20family%20and%20both%20Suprabha%20and%20Bijoya%20were%20trained%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERabindra%20Sangeet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Bijoya%2C%20a%20cousin%20of%20Satyajit%2C%20was%20not%20married%20to%20him%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20listen%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De7fk46fGxSY%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Bande%20Mataram%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGQpdlUmVZcI%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fe7fk46fGxSY%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20much%20do%20these%20recordings%20differ%20from%20what%20we%20know%20as%20the%20national%20anthem%3F%20There%20is%20no%20difference%2C%20except%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20version%20popular%20since%20the%20INA%E2%80%99s%20interventions%20is%20faster.%20By%20the%20time%20filmmaker%20Bimal%20Roy%20used%20the%20song%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%201944%20film%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EUdayer%20Pathe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20pace%20had%20already%20gone%20up.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2RGwAZi0c-o%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esame%20music%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20nonetheless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20may%20also%20compare%20all%20these%20renditions%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98authoritative%20version%E2%80%99%20recorded%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpL-U_bzs_yM%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPankaj%20Kumar%20Mullick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20early%201950s%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20request.%20This%20version%20was%20%E2%80%9Cplayed%20across%20the%20nation%20at%20almost%20every%20public%20place%20to%20familiarise%20every%20Indian%20citizen%20with%20the%20anthem%20of%20their%20newly%20formed%20independent%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpankajmullickfoundation.org%2Faboutpm%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Pankaj%20Mulluck%20Music%20and%20Arts%20Foundation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20compareit%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7ZHyVxrsOy4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EQaumi%20Tarana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20that%20Thakuri%20is%20said%20to%20have%20set%20to%20tune.%20This%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDDv8VEPvg-8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eanother%20recording%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20song%20released%20by%20Sansad%20TV.%20And%20here%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D216194643500540%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eanother%20version%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rendered%20by%20Lakshmi%20Sehgal%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20INA%20women%E2%80%99s%20wing%2C%20Rani%20Jhansi%20Brigade.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20truth%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianculture.gov.in%2Fnode%2F2834364%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20publicly%20sung%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%2026th%20session%20in%20Kolkata%20in%20December%201911.%20The%20singers%20included%20Sarala%20Devi%20Chaudhurani%2C%20Amal%20Home%2C%20and%20Chitralekha%20Siddhanta%2C%20among%20others.%20It%20was%20performed%20again%20at%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%201917%20session%20in%20Kolkata.%20However%2C%20no%20recording%20of%20these%20performances%20has%20been%20available.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201937%2C%20Congress%20adopted%20a%20truncated%20version%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Vande%20Mataram%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20national%20anthem%20among%20heated%20debates%20over%20the%20choice%20and%20song%20and%20whether%20the%20whole%20song%20or%20the%20truncated%20version%20would%20be%20adopted.%20The%20then%20Congress%20president%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20asked%20Bose%20to%20take%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20and%20Tagore%20favoured%20the%20truncated%20%E2%80%98Vande%20Mataram%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20his%20%E2%80%98great%20escape%E2%80%99%20from%20house%20arrest%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Bose%20reached%20Germany%20in%20April%201941%20and%20the%20Free%20India%20Centre%20was%20formally%20opened%20there%20in%20November%20when%20the%20Azad%20Hind%20Fauz%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netajisubhasbose.org%2Fhitler-s-germany-indian-legion%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eadopted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20national%20anthem.%20The%20Hamburg%20Radio%20Symphony%20Orchestra%20played%20the%20tune%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20anthem%20in%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia%2Fsome-facts-about-jana-gana-mana%2Fstory-y4Vo7YyapCob84DR8Op6jJ.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESeptember%201942%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Netaji%20researcher%20Anuj%20Dhar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanujdhar%2Fstatus%2F1486192469104816130%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshared%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20an%20audio%20clip%20of%20that%20recording.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20reaching%20Singapore%2C%20Netaji%20wanted%20a%20simpler%20version%20of%20the%20song%20written%20in%20Hindustani%2C%20which%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20Hindi%20and%20Urdu%20and%20which%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20language.%20That%20was%20when%20his%20close%20associate%20Abid%20Hassan%20and%20INA%20radio%E2%80%99s%20scriptwriter%20Mumtaz%20Hussain%20penned%20%E2%80%98Subh%20Sukh%20Chain%E2%80%99%20based%20on%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20lyrics.%20The%20music%20remained%20the%20same%2C%20though%20the%20Thakuri-led%20INA%20band%20paced%20it%20faster%20under%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20instruction%20to%20make%20it%20more%20suitable%20for%20a%20marching%20army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStories%20around%20Thakuri%20being%20the%20real%20composer%20of%20its%20music%20have%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20for%20over%2025%20years%20now.%20In%201997%2C%20Thakuri%2C%20then%20in%20his%2080s%2C%20claimed%20himself%20to%20be%20the%20composer%20of%20the%20music.%20On%20January%2023%2C%201997%2C%20an%20advertisement%20by%20the%20Gorkha%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(GNLF)-run%20Darjeeling%20Gorkha%20Hill%20Council%20in%20a%20Kolkata-based%20newspaper%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.rediff.com%2Fnews%2Ffeb%2F22anthem.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Thakuri%2C%20a%20Gorkha%2C%20to%20be%20the%20real%20music%20composer.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Thakuri%20also%20visited%20Darjeeling%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fstatue-stirs-up-anthem-debate%2Fcid%2F825815%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emade%20the%20claim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20event.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.rediff.com%2Ffreedom%2F19ram.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erepeated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20claim%20in%20media%20interviews%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20sometime%20in%201943%20in%20Rangoon%2C%20when%20Netaji%20called%20me%20over%20to%20say%20that%20a%20national%20anthem%20in%20Hindi%20was%20required%20for%20the%20provisional%20government%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%20Jana%20gana%20mana%20was%20in%20Bengali%2C%20so%20Netaji%2C%20Abid%20Hasan%2C%20and%20another%20person%20got%20together%20to%20translate%20it.%20Subsequently%2C%20it%20was%20given%20to%20me%20and%20I%20set%20it%20to%20music%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.rediff.com%2Fnews%2Fapr%2F26anthem.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20Gorkha%20politicians%20of%20Darjeeling%20have%20kept%20the%20issue%20alive%2C%20and%20so%20have%20a%20section%20of%20people%20around%20Himachal.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20website%20named%20Indian%20Gorkhas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiangorkhas.in%2F2016%2F01%2Fvideo-proof-capt-ram-singh-thakuri-gave.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecited%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20video%20of%20Tagore%20reciting%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20to%20claim%20that%20it%20conclusively%20proved%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%E2%80%99%20was%20different.%20They%20were%20completely%20oblivious%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Tagore%20was%20reciting%20it%2C%20not%20singing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThakuri%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20%E2%80%98Kadam%20Kadam%20Badhaye%20Ja%E2%80%99%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20popular%20patriotic%20songs%2C%20died%20in%202002.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692538247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F20171201%2FIndian_National_Flag.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fits-time-to-end-all-speculations-about-the-composer-of-jana-gana-manas-music%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22INA%20Captain%20Ram%20Singh%20Thakuri%20continues%20to%20be%20credited%20for%20setting%20its%20tune%20despite%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20composing%20both%20lyrics%20and%20the%20music.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fits-time-to-end-all-speculations-about-the-composer-of-jana-gana-manas-music%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%