bours%20told%20us%20that%20another%20family%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20attacked%20the%20couple%20with%20iron%20rods.%20The%20couple%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20We%20are%20getting%20the%20post-mortem%20done.%20A%20police%20force%20has%20been%20deployed%20in%20the%20villag%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sitapur%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Chakresh%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interfaith%20couple%2C%20whose%20location%20the%20police%20has%20not%20revealed%2C%20is%20reportedly%20under%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20couple%20eloped%20in%202020%2C%20the%20woman%20had%20reportedly%20been%20a%20minor.%20The%20man%20was%20then%20booked%20under%20charges%20of%20kidnapping%2C%20rape%2C%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act.%20When%20the%20woman%20turned%2018%2C%20they%20eloped%20again%2C%20and%20she%20gave%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20court%20that%20she%20was%20leaving%20her%20family%20of%20her%20own%20volition%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20son%2C%2028%2C%20of%20the%20deceased%20couple%2C%20was%20booked%20in%202020%20for%20eloping%20with%20a%20minor%20girl.%20The%20case%20was%20lodged%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20received%20from%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20family.%20He%20was%20subsequently%20arrested%20and%20spent%2013%20months%20in%20jail.%20A%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20girl%20turned%2018%20and%20became%20an%20adult%20and%20the%20two%20again%20ran%20away.%20Another%20case%20was%20lodged%20and%20they%20were%20found%2C%20but%20this%20time%20the%20girl%20gave%20a%20statement%20in%20court%20in%20favour%20of%20her%20partner.%20The%20man%20was%20again%20arrested%20around%20two%20months%20ago%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20separate%20case%20and%20released%20on%20bail%20just%20a%20few%20days%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692534155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content