0in%20a%20better%20way%20they%20would%20not%20require%20tutoring.%20But%20my%20father%20was%20so%20angry%20at%20my%20decision%20that%20he%20stopped%20speaking%20to%20me.%20If%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20bedroom%2C%20he%20would%20move%20to%20the%20drawing-room%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20continued%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20no%20one%20should%20quit%20on%20their%20dreams.%20Dreams%20have%20the%20power%20to%20become%20reality.%20This%20kept%20me%20motivated%20when%20my%20father%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20me.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20took%20a%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20work%20I%20do.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20we%20invited%20former%20vice%20president%20M%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%20for%20a%20project%20launch%2C%20my%20father%20also%20joined%20us%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20He%20understood%20that%20I%20was%20serious%20about%20the%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327625%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20the%20govt%20school%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20launching%20the%20non-profit%2C%20Abhishek%20started%20his%20journey%20with%20a%20government%20school%20for%20girls.%20Talking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%20in%202017%2C%20there%20were%20only%2079%20girls%20enrolled%20in%20the%20school.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20with%20the%20school%20to%20transform%20the%20education%20system%20with%20digital%20learning%20methods%2C%20the%20enrollment%20of%20girls%20increased%20to%20129.%20This%20impact%20encouraged%20us%20to%20understand%20that%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20is%20meaningful%20for%20the%20children%20in%20the%20government%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20kick%20off%20the%20work%2C%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20Muskaan%20Dreams%20signs%20an%20MoU%20(Memorandum%20of%20Understanding)%20with%20the%20state%20governments%20for%20a%20particular%20period.%20Thereafter%2C%20they%20conduct%20in-person%20meetings%20with%20district%20collectors%20who%20help%20them%20select%20government%20schools%20in%20rural%20areas%20based%20on%20the%20power%20availability%20to%20run%20the%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20arrange%20meetings%20with%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20engage%20them%20in%20discussions%20about%20the%20benefits%20and%20opportunities%20that%20lie%20ahead.%20It%20helps%20build%20enthusiasm%20and%20commitment%20among%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20ensure%20their%20active%20involvement%20in%20the%20implementation%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20collaborating