20to%20teachers%20to%20ensure%20the%20adoption%20of%20technology%20in%20teaching%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20is%20divided%20into%20four%20modules%20that%20are%20mandatory%20for%20each%20teacher%20to%20attend.%20We%20make%20our%20teachers%20familiar%20with%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20digital%20lesson%2C%20teaching%2C%20and%20learning%20models%20using%20technology%20and%20methods%20of%20delivering%20instruction.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20invest%20in%20teacher%20training%20to%20foster%20a%20stronger%20education%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20informs%20that%20his%20team%20works%20with%20any%20school%20for%202-3%20years.%20After%20they%20leave%2C%20they%20provide%20virtual%20tech%20support%20to%20ensure%20teachers%20are%20ensuring%20the%20consistency%20of%20digital%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20we%20stop%20hand%20holding%20the%20schools%2C%20we%20try%20to%20build%20capacity%20to%20lower%20dependency%20on%20our%20team%20so%20they%20remain%20efficient%20post-exit.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20we%20have%20engaged%20private%20organisations%20like%20Pernod%20Ricard%20India%20Foundation%2C%20LTI%20Mindtree%2C%20Yash%20Technologies%2C%20and%20Acuity%20Knowledge%20Partners%20who%20offer%20resources%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20funding%20to%20support%20the%20sustainability%20of%20our%20initiative%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%981%20Million%20by%202025%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20says%20that%20every%20year%2C%20they%20conduct%20an%20annual%20survey%20to%20understand%20the%20experience%20of%20children%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F105260%2Findia-literacy-project-interactive-learning-rural-government-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D