EExplaining%20the%20challenge%20to%20ensure%20schools%20continue%20to%20use%20digital%20means%20after%20they%20leave%2C%20he%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20external%20organisation%2C%20we%20cannot%20guarantee%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20actions%20once%20our%20direct%20engagement%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%20But%20we%20track%20the%20usage%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251330%2Fprabhat-saxena-uttar-pradesh-iit-srijan-ek-soch-ngo-rural-india-education-underprivileged-smart-classes-shiksha-ki-gadi-upliftment-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20TVs%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20digital%20tools%20through%20regular%20evaluations.%20We%20also%20assist%20schools%20with%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20digital%20infrastructure.%20We%20strive%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20where%20smart%20TVs%20and%20digital%20tools%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20educational%20practices.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20initiative%2C%20Abhishek%20does%20not%20charge%20any%20fee%20from%20the%20students.%20The%20expenses%20are%20managed%20through%20funds%20from%20CSR%20activities%20and%20corporate%20collaborations%20from%20partners%20like%20Amazon%20India%2C%20Linkedin%2C%20ONGC%2C%20and%20Hindustan%20Zinc.%20To%20further%20the%20cause%2C%20he%20is%20planning%20to%20expand%20the%20project%20to%20Karnataka%20schools%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%20and%20reach%20out%20to%201%20million%20students%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20big%20goals%20ahead%2C%20Abhishek%20speaks%20about%20the%20decision%20he%20took%20years%20back%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20was%20placed%20in%20any%20company%20like%20my%20friends%2C%20I%20would%20be%20just%20another%20corporate%20employee.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20took%20a%20stand.%20Whatever%20happened%2C%20happened%20for%20a%20good%20reason.%20Although%20we%20work%2010-12%20hours%20daily%2C%20I%20cherish%20