%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327144%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20catch%20Navin%20Noronha%E2%80%99s%20shows%20in%20these%20cities%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERisque%20comedy%2C%20hope%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20creating%20a%20haven%20for%20queer%20people%20who%20can%20just%20laugh%20and%20be%20themselves%2C%20Navin%20has%20built%20a%20special%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CQueer%20people%20are%20bringing%20other%20queer%20people%20to%20my%20shows.%20My%20special%20sold%20out%20primarily%20through%20word%20of%20mouth%20because%20half%20the%20people%20at%20the%20show%20were%20queer.%20Apart%20from%20my%20solo%20shows%2C%20when%20we%20do%20the%20line-up%20shows%2C%20more%20people%20show%20up%20because%20of%20the%20diversity%20in%20the%20lineup%20and%20the%20other%20comics%20bring%20in%20their%20fanbase%20too.%20We%20have%20comics%20from%20across%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20spectrum%2C%20and%20the%20scene%20is%20developing%20for%20the%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20also%20sees%20hope%20in%20the%20younger%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CUnlike%20our%20generation%20(millennials)%2C%20Gen%20Zs%20have%20their%20photo%2C%20biodata%2C%20Instagram%20link%2C%20Spotify%20link%20and%20somet